sub_title: Interested in renewable energy, palaeoenvironmental changes, climate change and biodiversity.
summary:
SUMMARY	
Professional experience of fifteen years in petroleum consulting (exploration and development geology) and scientific research (geomorphology, tectonics and geochronology), recently renewable energy and agriculture. Humanitarian voluntary experience of five years (goods- and fundraiser for Romanian children, family integration in Netherlands).   

INTEREST 	
Nature-based and technical solutions to resolve complex natural resource, environmental and societal challenges. With focus on natural energy resources (renewable and water included), natural hazards, fault compartmentalisation, carbon storage, water and climate, river dynamics. Combining earth observation, seismic interpretation, in-situ and laboratory observations with project management, geodata analysis and modelling.
